snippet.title: Ace Combat 7: Skies Unknown - PS4/XB1/PC - Gamescom 2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for take-off? ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN launches January 18th on PlayStation 4 and Xbox One and on February 1st on PC via Steam!
